Unitron/Firestarter/Sixshot/Ares/Double Punch/Manterror/Bumblebee/Injector:




Bumblebee hit the ground like a sack of bricks, dead.

Unitron gave a final shout and less than two seconds later the remaining 
seven robots blew apart in a grand self destruct sequence that blew their 
bodies into unrecognizable scrap, along with Bumblebee's.
